title: My daughter’s birthday treat!
text: I took my family to our neighborhood Outback for my daughter’s birthday (March 21st) and we all enjoyed great meals of medallions, a ribeye and my prime rib.  The service by our waitress Hanna was impeccable, and she was very sweet to offer my daughter a birthday cheesecake desert on the house!  After dinner, the manager Phil stopped by to see if we were happy with the service and food, and we conversed awhile on our satisfaction with our “Outback” outing.  Thanks to Phil, Hanna and team for a great experience!  We’ll be back soon because you guys ROCK!
